{"tid":1722950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（誠哥又出手）港燈：中小型食肆客戶可以遲兩個月先交電費","createTime":"2019-11-15T04:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:38:22.000Z","uid":36494,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0bb475ac4a253bf6b00f43b69b0179429fc48a","tid":1722950,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"港燈表示，鑑於中小企餐飲業受近期社會事件衝擊較大，而電費佔經營開支比例較其他行業相對高，港燈將稍後發信邀請合資格的商戶參加。<br />\n<br />\n所有位處港燈供電範圍、符合中小企定義即僱用少於50人、持有有效商業登記及飲食業牌照的食肆，均可申請把12月以及明年1月份的電費，延期2個月繳交。"},{"pid":"b9d27fec470b629e1631cf358c3e51197e3ddccf","tid":1722950,"uid":82829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"錢魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e2b019b2ac07fefacd8c43b5b4c182f0bf3235","tid":1722950,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哥"},{"pid":"beadebe88ef781c2d5d201a5e42c846458543e22","tid":1722950,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"[內附名單][重要]各大學據點請主動出擊！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722838</a>"},{"pid":"136b7f60db0a7bcf9df73bb75d0f0d27e8c01b4e","tid":1722950,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"誠哥太屈機<br />\n<br />\n最強黃絲"},{"pid":"3365ab4df4470f59004f36ad44989ff410150fc5","tid":1722950,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f42cb3aa473f1d392499b3becd26b940f85be12","tid":1722950,"uid":119250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"係就減價或者唔洗交啦"},{"pid":"0e92e435b2fd32b0c